author: Four fellows from Finland
title: Four fellows from Finland
text: Our driver was waiting for us at the Munich airport as agreed and drove us to our hotel at Saalbach fast and safe. On our way back to Munich one of us forgot his mobile phone at the car, but the driver brought it back to the airport. Excellent service!
